PWS Connect Privacy Policy
User's guide
At bog bridges, ensuring the privacy of our users is of utmost importance. We will never share or sell your data, and we will not allow ads to be displayed in our apps.
​
The Privacy Policy for the PWS Connect Apple Watch and Apple iPhone apps is simple.
​
The app does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable Information (PII) from users of the app, and does not knowingly share any data with advertisers or any other third parties.
​
PWS Connect uses secure Internet-based communications solely to obtain weather station data, and to access Apple's App Store functionality. Location information is used only to help locate available weather stations near you via third party weather service APIs.
​
If you have additional questions or require more information about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through email at
info@bogbridges.com
​
Consent
​
By using the PWS Connect app, you hereby consent to this Privacy Policy and agree to its Terms and Conditions.